s genetic code linked to parkinsons the new york times retrieved september     dynamodata    young innovators under  sergey brin  technology review  retrieved august     brin and page awarded mbas press release september     local business leaders receive awards for their success in business and the community  local business leaders receive awards for their success in business pr newswire  june  web  apr    academy achievement golden plate   the worlds most powerful people  sergey brin and larry page forbes november    national academy of engineering press release february    national science foundation fellow profiles  sergey brin forbes october   retrieved october    external linksedit find more aboutsergey brinat wikipedias sister projects media from commons quotations from wikiquote googlecom – sergey brin sergey brin at ted appearances on cspan sergey brin on charlie rose sergey brin on imdb sergey brin collected news and commentary bloomberg news  sergey brin collected news and commentary the guardian  sergey brin collected news and commentary the new york times  sergey brin collected news and commentary the wall street journal  profile sergey brin at bbc news sergey brin at forbes sergey brin at bloomberg lp momentmag the story of sergey brin biography portal business and economics portal film portal google portal internet portal judaism portal literature portal maryland portal russia portal science portal v t e alphabet inc divisions google access calico capitalg deepmind gv jigsaw nest sidewalk verily x waymo people arthur d levinson astro teller david krane eric schmidt ruth porat sundar pichai tony fadell andrew conrad founders larry page sergey brin category portal task force v t e google overview alphabet inc history list of mergers and acquisitions by alphabet products criticism privacy concerns censorship easter eggs dont be evil advertising admob adscape adsense adwords analytics contributor partners doubleclick doubleclick for publishers wallet comm