w goal make everything work together the search giant has found a new purpose in all our lives bringing together the various products and services we use to work together as easily as possible articleby nick stattmay    pm pdt google glass just couldnt handle the stress the search giants wearable headset was plagued by numerous problems including an excess of attention for a product that wasnt ready for a massmarket audience according to the new york times articleby nick stattfebruary    pm pst show more hot products amazon dash wand with alexa  amazons alexaenabled dash wand is fun and nearly free msrp  samsung galaxy s a month later the galaxy s is still pretty freaking awesome  oneplus  the affordable oneplus  impresses us again apple ipad  inch apples new inch ipad is a great tablet at a great price  microsoft surface pro  still a pro despite an unadventurous update  best list find the best hybrids on the market hybrid technology can be applied to any type of car and the best show the most significant fuel economy improvements over a similar gasolineonly car show me now tags  cnet cnet tags cnet special topics most popular tags facebook samsung amazon sony stephen hawking hillary clinton vladimir putin donald trump browse all tags a b c d e f g h i j k l m n o p q r s t u v w x y z a abc acer activision acura adam savage adele adobe adobe creative cloud advertising aereo airbnb airbus airplay alan turing alcatel onetouch alexa alfa romeo alibaba alphabet inc amazon amazon prime amd american express andrew mason android jelly bean android kitkat android lollipop android marshmallow android nougat android o android pay android wear animation anonymous antisec antitrust aol apple homekit apple maps apple music apple pay archaeology arm artificial intelligence ashton kutcher asio aston martin asus att audi browse all tags a b c d e f g h i j k l m n o p q r s t u v w x y z this week on cnet news see all cartoon bunnies are hacking your brain virtual reality apps whe