ices with which i could easily look at such a book it would have saved me a lot of time and it would have spared google a tremendous amount of effort sergey brin time effort book if google books is successful others will follow sergey brin successful google follow share this page cite this page citation find on amazon sergey brin related authors steve jobs warren buffett henry ford bill gates jim rohn stephen covey peter drucker les brown brainyquote desktop brainyquote mobile site home authors topics quote of the day pictures top  quotes professions birthdays social bq on facebook bq on twitter bq on pinterest bq on google bq on instagram shop brainyquote store apps iphoneipad app quote of the day feeds javascript and rss feeds wordpress plugin quote of the day email about about us contact us submit privacy terms copyright     brainyquote   loading load more quotes